{"tid":601809,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國、美日調查同稱　香港淪朝突破制裁「中間人」","createTime":"2018-03-22T13:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T01:53:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"35501f4ebd8637700925a0c55c788413ef85ba0b","tid":601809,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/photo/bknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180322144755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180322144755&h=a65586d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美聯社報道，聯合國、美國及日本調查發現，香港淪為北韓走私違禁貨物的中間人。由於香港成立公司手續迅速簡易，加上有大量經紀協助作企業登記，成為北韓突破制裁的缺口，美國已向香港政府要求加強打擊有關交易。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，聯合國在近日的監察北韓制裁效果報告中稱，與北韓有關的企業以「迴避手段」，包括在香港設立表面上的公司作遮掩，來避過制裁。有不少經紀公司代這些企業作登記，是國際對北韓制裁行動的主要缺口。當中有許多公司，亦與中國內地有關聯。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社指，香港經常在最自由經濟體中排名第一，城內有大量熟悉商業登記的專家，能在客戶給予最少資料的情況下，迅速為企業登記，甚至有透過互聯網就可一日內開公司的服務。這一方面便利貿易，另一方面卻助長非法行動。<br />\n<br />\n在去年12月，南韓曾截獲一艘香港登記、疑向北韓船隻私運燃油的貨船，自此國際就留意到香港公司在北韓突破制裁活動上所扮演的角色。在上月被美國列入新制裁名單的11間公司中，有5間就是來自香港，中國內地、台灣各有兩間，新加坡及巴拿馬各一間。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社近日到其中一間被美國制裁的香港公司、利百船務有限公司的登記地址查詢，職員稱已終止與利百船務合作，拒絕進一步回應。而早前被日本自衞隊拍得與北韓船隻交接的伯利茲旗船隻Wan heng 11號，登記持有人為中國內地船公司Zhejiang Wanheng，在香港亦有多個相關登記地址，職員同樣拒絕回應美聯社提問。<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部官員早前表示，香港境內有不少北韓的洗錢及走私活動，已在會議上要求香港政府官員加強打擊。港府在聲明中表示，高度關注違反制裁令的可疑事件及活動，正在觀察與香港註冊公司有關的個案。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/photo/bknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001_02p.jpg?20180322144755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180322144755&h=fe4b2ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合國（右上）報告指，香港成為北韓突破制裁的「中間人」。左上為被揭向北韓走私的香港登記駁船。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001.html&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1KS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=a49e99c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bknint-20180322131317784-0322_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9296fc32982f7ed401b1424a2886a7418bc5ec01","tid":601809,"uid":6604,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"如果香港政策法保唔住<br />\n真係要諗下離開自己出生同成長嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c45adfa6f9594bc549215d4ec8dcbee7244b040","tid":601809,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"香港變公廁"},{"pid":"6cdfb58653c9169cc5611c355ecd85aabb3ad521","tid":601809,"uid":63670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0890781fbefa9bc870ea106fadce95098d770f","tid":601809,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"制裁埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f0b97558bcfc841afc0cf44783dccc2378b25e","tid":601809,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係做走私水貨生意架喇"},{"pid":"c812e0d83d2c972c07199b7c599de3542d60739f","tid":601809,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>制裁埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n制裁緊, 陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdfa940501a52d2d61178741f8a22aa77ae063e","tid":601809,"uid":150902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:47:46.000Z","msg":"香港唔做走私過水邊得今時今日?"},{"pid":"1cccaccf26059e3bb188297ca6c2aa60082016e2","tid":601809,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c812e0d83d2c972c07199b7c599de3542d60739f","tid":601809,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>制裁埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n制裁緊, 陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c387ba2b9113c20829ee6ba525791635f2a295","tid":601809,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"香港本身個定位就係做中間人"},{"pid":"65d326970e2f91d0f95ae7bf8c2a1c7d6d476611","tid":601809,"uid":3773,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:01:30.000Z","msg":"香港=中朝安全套"},{"pid":"523f15a039ed79050a12cadad1769e75779c18b7","tid":601809,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"臭閪港不嬲係世界賤雞<br />\n任屌無套三穴中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3acac36cf4bf83dde8e179a86bafba8d67b676d","tid":601809,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"愛國商人"},{"pid":"a4d272f2ba3972ae1fc1047965687c9ffec1000b","tid":601809,"uid":84013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:29:33.000Z","msg":"《香港01》報道，該船由一間香港空殼公司持有，唯一董事和股東是一名叫龔銳強的<span style=\"color: red;\">廣州人</span>。連同永嘉，龔在香港共擁有5間公司，分別為方向海運發展（香港）有限公司丶方向海運發展有限公司丶方向海運管理有限公司丶安理達有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n龔於大陸也持有多間船務公司。根據龔旗下公司的網上招聘資料，方向海運承運東南亞航線為主的棕櫚油等化學品。國際調查記者聯盟（ICIJ）資料顯示，龔銳強2005年在英屬處女群島註冊公司，但於2008年停止運作。"},{"pid":"8b1813896738aef61bd0a01aaeabc349707ebc27","tid":601809,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"講真無大陸背景香港應該都搞唔起依種走私"},{"pid":"0ba8407f7883077d9820973372fb76a12fcfc7a8","tid":601809,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9296fc32982f7ed401b1424a2886a7418bc5ec01","tid":601809,"uid":6604,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"如果香港政策法保唔住<br />\n真係要諗下離開自己出生同成長嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951830936c733db704aa9416152dc66e8f1ffebb","tid":601809,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"睇黎香港刧數難逃，老美實引爆香港收鄰國皮"},{"pid":"e5c14dcd0c39d2fd7bce70ad198795e86f776d41","tid":601809,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:36:00.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815c27a34b96fb284faeecef1187f4a3f6a1175d","tid":601809,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9296fc32982f7ed401b1424a2886a7418bc5ec01","tid":601809,"uid":6604,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"如果香港政策法保唔住<br />\n真係要諗下離開自己出生同成長嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"日本外相擬本月下旬訪港　就制裁北韓謀求合作<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386751-20180319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386751-20180319.htm&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1KS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=bb4bf0d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386751-20180319.htm&h=41f7f498\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386751-20180319.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，日本外相河野太郎計劃本月下旬訪問香港，期間會與行政長官林鄭月娥會談，討論合作制裁北韓，確保嚴格履行檢查船隻等措施。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，有關方面去年12月曾發現香港註冊船隻，在海上將精煉石油產品，轉移至北韓船隻。<br />\n<br />\n共同社又說，河野太郎還會要求本港，撤銷在東日本大地震後對日本食品實施的進口限制；另外，東京會在2020年主辦奧運，河野將與本港官員，就香港人到日本旅遊的問題交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n安倍訪美行程推遲至下月中旬<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=998768&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D998768%26csid%3D261_367&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1KS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=986e76cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=998768&amp;csid=261_367</a><br />\n<br />\n日本媒體報道，首相安倍晉三的訪美行程將會推遲至下月中旬。美日雙方早前同意安倍下月初到訪美國，與總統特朗普見面，在兩韓及美朝首腦會談前，商討為達至半島無核化的應對方針。有日本官員透露安倍推遲訪美，是因為特朗普下月初的日程安排不方便。報道指，日美首腦會談將會確認對北韓繼續施加最大壓力，直到北韓有邁向無核化的具體行動，日方亦會再度要求美方協助解決日本人被綁架的問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，南韓總統文在寅在總統府青瓦台出席內閣會議時說，平昌冬奧與冬殘奧緩和兩韓關係，向全世界傳遞和平信息，實現兩韓首腦及美朝首腦會談，開創半島和平的道路，要確保一切的正面轉變維持下去。<br />\n<br />\n如果林鄭唔配合制裁北韓，安倍可能響Trump面前參香港一本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1083182a5b36db4e0719050e9ed8c7c1b755ef2","tid":601809,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"523f15a039ed79050a12cadad1769e75779c18b7","tid":601809,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"臭閪港不嬲係世界賤雞<br />\n任屌無套三穴中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff160f58f1ec97da4e0203406e957cf34624c9f","tid":601809,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"要自保慢慢玩就一定要做野比人睇,<br />\n不過而家班官一d遠見都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}